title: Bradford trade & 2016 QB Rankings
itunes:title: Bradford trade & 2016 QB Rankings
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Chris Wesseling– analyze the latest NFL news including the Vikings trading for QB Sam Bradford and the Eagles announcing QB Carson Wentz as their Week 1 starter. Then the heroes weigh in on Jared Goff being named the No. 3 QB for the Rams before wrapping the podcast sharing their Pre-Week 1 QB rankings.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
